The Pan Africanist Congress of Azania will celebrate Sobukwe Month by hosting a gala dinner at Langa Sports Complex on Saturday February 25. Keynote address will be given by Professor Sipho Shabalala and the theme of the night is “Untamed in Life , Victorius in Death”. The uncaptured life and times of this giant son of the soil, Robert Sobukwe will be laid bare. For more details contact Sindile Moya at 0793736541 or Yandiswa Filipe at 0743890103. 24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.  